    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small disposable cubes containing a bulb and reflector on four sides that provides four flashes in rapid succession, powered by battery and a circuit in a camera through current pulses. These have become obsolete with the advent of electronic flash.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
